sequenceDiagram
    actor CC as Caisse Centrale
    participant UI as Frontend
    participant API as API Requests
    participant DB as Base Données
    participant Notif as Notifications
    
    CC->>UI: Clique "Valider"
    UI->>UI: Dialog confirmation
    CC->>UI: Confirme
    UI->>API: POST /api/requests/[id]/validate
    API->>API: Vérifier authz (CC role)
    API->>DB: Vérifier status = SUBMITTED
    alt Status valide
        API->>DB: UPDATE status=VALIDATED
        API->>DB: SET validatedBy, validatedAt
        API->>DB: INSERT ActionLog
        DB-->>API: Confirmé
        API->>Notif: Notifier Tunisie Sécurité
        API-->>UI: Request validée
        UI-->>CC: Toast succès
    else Status invalide
        API-->>UI: Erreur 400
        UI-->>CC: Message erreur
    end
